Time / Date Stamp functions related to the action of the functions, by providing the relationship to command and control.

td.time - records network time from NIST or USNO Master Clock
td.date - records network date from NIST or USNO Master Clock
td.history - records a log of access control of network time from NIST or USNO Master Clock

****************************************************************
Karchain functions related to the OCP network platform. [Karchain is our version of Blockchain but for autos]
****Due to Security issues - select code & functions will not be release to the public****

kc.info - OCP KC:Karchain matrix [list of definitions & functions]
kc.ai - OCP AI:artificial intelligence matrix [list of definitions & functions]
kc.func - list of function definitions
kc.health - Network status of OCP KC  
kc.health.ai - Network status of OCP AI on KC
kc.sec.health - Security status of the OCP KC network both internal and external 

****************************************************************
Insurance Smart Contract code related to the OCP Karchain network platform.

acronym:isc: Insurance Smart Contract

info:isc command and control

isc.info - isc matrix [list of definitions]
isc.ai - OCP AI:artificial intelligence matrix [list of definitions]
isc.owner - members policy information [name, address, contact, policy number and policy type]
isc.policy - type of policy
isc.cdate - creation date of the policy [the day the policy was made and executed]
isc.ctime - creation time of the policy [the time the policy was made and executed]
isc.cost - cost of policy ownership [total cost of the policy to the member and OCP]
isc.access - who access to the insurance smart contract [command and control access]
isc.status - status of the policy [open or closed]
isc.balance - members remaining policy balance [balance based on the time of request]
isc.transfer - members transfer from bank to wallet
isc.history - members insurance smart contract history [all payments made since day one of opening account]
isc.location - where the insurance policy is located and based [state, city or region based using USPS FIPS & ZipCode+4] 
isc.duration - how long the insurance policy is in force [by numerial months]
isc.release - when a payment will be released for payment [expected release date shown]
isc.destroy - when and how the policy will be cancelled [expected policy end date & cause]
isc.penalty - what and how the penalty will be imposed to the policy holder [expected the penalty cost and amount returned to member]
isc.dmv - status of the policy holders dmv records and matrix [open or closed] 
isc.library - OCP isc data code library

payment:incoming

isc.payment - payment matrix [list of definitions]
isc.payment.ai - OCP AI:artificial intelligence matrix [list of definitions]
isc.payment.amount - members monthly payment amount [either in KarTokens or USD and any other currencies]
isc.payment.type - payment & currency type
isc.payment.owner - members payment information [wallet or bank name, address, contact, policy number and policy type]
isc.payment.time - time stamp of the payment made
isc.payment.date - date stamp of the payment made
isc.payment.access - list of who has access to payments
isc.payment.status - the status of payments either accepted, pending or declined states
isc.payment.balance - members remaining payment balance [balance based on the time of request]
isc.payment.transfer - members payment transfer from bank to wallet
isc.payment.history - members payment history [all payments made since day one of opening account]
isc.payment.location - where the payment is coming from
isc.payment.duration - how long the payment is in force
isc.payment.release - when a payment will be released for payment
isc.payment.destroy - when and how the payment will be cancelled
isc.payment.returned - when and how the payment will be returned to the member
isc.payment.penalty - when a payment will be assessed based on the penalty from dmv records poll
isc.payment.dmv - status assessed based on the penalty from dmv records poll
isc.payment.library - OCP isc payment data code library

claims:payments outgoing

isc.payout - claims matrix [list of definitions]
isc.payout.ai - OCP AI:artificial intelligence matrix [list of definitions]
isc.payout.amount - ocp claim amount [either in KarTokens or USD and any other currencies]
isc.payout.type - payments made to settle claims
isc.payout.owner - who gets ocp payout payment [wallet or bank name, address, contact, policy number and policy type]
isc.payout.time - ocp claim time stamp of payment made
isc.payout.date - ocp claim date stamp of payment made
isc.payout.access - list of who has access to payout payments
isc.payout.status - status of the payout claim [open or closed]
isc.payout.balance - total claim payouts made to date
isc.payout.transfer - ocp claim payment transfer from bank to wallet
isc.payout.history - ocp claim payment history [ocp payments made since day one of member opening account]
isc.payout.location - where the claim payment is coming from
isc.payout.duration - how long the claim payment is in force
isc.payout.release - when a claim payment will be released for payment
isc.payout.destroy - when and how the claim payment will be cancelled
isc.payout.returned - when and how the payout will be returned to the insurance smart contract
isc.payout.penalty - when a payment will be assessed based on the penalty from dmv records poll
isc.payout.dmv - status assessed based on the penalty from dmv records poll
isc.payout.library - OCP isc payout data code library

penalty:imposed

isc.penalty - penalty matrix [list of definitions]
isc.penalty.ai - OCP AI:artificial intelligence matrix [list of definitions]
isc.penalty.amount - amount of penalty imposed
isc.penalty.type - type of penalty imposed
isc.penalty.owner - ocp payment information [wallet or bank name, address, contact, policy number and policy type]
isc.penalty.pct - percentage of penalty imposed
isc.penalty.time - penalty time stamp of payment made
isc.penalty.date - penalty date stamp of payment made
isc.penalty.access - list of who has access to the penalty
isc.penalty.status - status of the penalty [open or closed]
isc.penalty.balance - total balance of the penalty made to date
isc.penalty.transfer - penalty payment transfer from bank to wallet
isc.penalty.history - penalty payment history [ocp payments made since day one of member opening account]
isc.penalty.location - where the penalty payment is coming from
isc.penalty.duration - how long the penalty is in force
isc.penalty.release - when a penalty payment will be released for payment
isc.penalty.destroy - when and how the penalty will be cancelled
isc.penalty.returned - when and how the payment will be returned to the member
isc.penalty.dmv - status assessed based on the penalty matrix from dmv records poll
isc.penalty.library - OCP isc penalty data code library

payback:policy cancellation or account closure/refunds

isc.payback - payout matrix [list of definitions]
isc.payback.ai - OCP AI:artificial intelligence matrix [list of definitions]
isc.payback.amount - ocp payback payment amount [total amount]
isc.payback.type - payback payments type to be made to member
isc.payback.owner - who gets the payback payment [wallet or bank name, address, contact, policy number and policy type]
isc.payback.pct - percentage of payback imposed
isc.payback.time - ocp payback payment time stamp of payment made
isc.payback.date - ocp payback payment date stamp of payment made
isc.payback.access - list of who has access to the payback access [who made the payback payment]
isc.payback.status - status of the payback payment [open or closed]
isc.payback.balance - total balance on the payback made to date
isc.payback.transfer - ocp payback payment transfer from bank to wallet
isc.payback.history - ocp payback payment history [ocp payments made since day one of member opening account]
isc.payback.location - where the payback payment is coming from
isc.payback.duration - how long the payback payment is in force
isc.payback.release - when a payback payment will be released for payment
isc.payback.destroy - when and how the payback payment will be cancelled
isc.payback.returned - when and how the payback payment will be returned to the insurance smart contract
isc.payback.library - OCP isc payback data code library
